Module com.example.manage_inventory
Package com.example.manage_inventory.Controller

Class ModProductController

java.lang.Object
com.example.manage_inventory.Controller.ModProductController
All Implemented Interfaces:
javafx.fxml.Initializable
public class ModProductController extends Object implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
Controller for modifying products in the inventory management app. Handles user input, validates data, and saves or cancels modifications. Provides functionality for adding, removing, and searching associated parts. FUTURE ENHANCEMENT: Implementing search functionality for parts can enhance the user experience by allowing users to quickly find and associate specific parts with the product being modified, improving the efficiency of the modification process.
